There are also pieces of tofu that appear to be glazed with a dark sauce, likely hoisin and sriracha as mentioned in the caption. The dish is presented in a white bowl.
The image shows a close-up of Singapore noodles with vegetables (broccoli, carrots, peas, green peppers) and what appears to be tofu.
The image shows a close-up of vegan lemon crinkle cookies with lemons in the background. The caption mentions that the recipe is courtesy of @thelittleblogofvegan.
The image shows two trays of vegan cinnamon rolls being drizzled with icing. The post mentions the recipe being from Buzzfeed Tasty and Merleeshay.
The image shows a Caesar salad with vegan bacon and dressing. The poster, tennilleamy.food, mentions using @madewithplants bacon and @colessupermarkets vegan caesar dressing.
The image shows a Starbucks Frappuccino with plant-based whipped cream. The photo appears to be taken inside a shopping mall, with a Christmas tree visible in the background.
